iv><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/uwIvqmA.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9YQwSKn.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LOsoTof.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/RcZBXOn</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CrimsonPermanentAssurance]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>This would play</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/OXm1g5W</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eYUPDUJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/OXm1g5W</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GullahGullahIslander]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>And unclench your jaw</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Ohw5eA4</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KXBLrAW.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Ohw5eA4</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GullahGullahIslander]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I think we’re on to something.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/LNvfhgf</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/j126PH8.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/LNvfhgf</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheGhostOfAkistos]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>October Plans [OC]</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Tryy486</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MkAMCae.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wZcUcSR.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Get your NEW Joel slogan t-shirts and hats here: https://litterboxcomics.shop/collections/pickleball-is-a-psyop</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0UeeHP6.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.patreon.com/litterboxcomics</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Tryy486</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LitterboxComics]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>We're on the edge of losing it all</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4IWIKvZ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xrzdmI9.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If we haven't already lost it all, we're right on the edge.

It's time to do absolutely everything we can to save our democracy.

If there's a vote, vote Democrat. I don't care how lame they are, they are the only non-fascist option that has any hope of winning any election. I don't care what lame excuse you have for not voting or voting third-party, at this point, anyone who isn't voting Democrat is SUPPORTING FASCISM. And speaking as a progressive with vanishingly little representation in this country, it sucks. But I vote Dem because it's the only sane thing to do.

If there's a protest, get out if you can. I'm a wheelchair user and I can't always, but I am when I can. Protest by itself does little, same with talking about these issues: But talking builds community, protest shows people are willing to get out there and speak up. These are necessary foundational steps to what we need to do, which is to take action and make changes. So these things are critical.

We need to use every single tool at our disposal against fascism. The norms are already gone. I don't like violene; I don't like politics; but you know what I hate more? Fascism.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/4IWIKvZ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[daychilde]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The same people who threw a fit about wearing a mask in 2020...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/AfDmd0B</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/v6GWPxm.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/AfDmd0B</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CptCheesePants]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Empty and blindsided. Mom's gone.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/mvjj0UB</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XwBRauz.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Can't pull enough together for a detailed post. Dad called me up just before midnight his time to tell me EMS and the police arrived. Mom suffered her first and only heart attack just a couple hours after she fell asleep. She had a class full of 2nd graders that had to learn a horrible life lesson that morning. We're still trying to get everything set up now that Dad's alone and her side of the family is throwing a fit she didn't want a funeral. I just finished writing her obituary. It's a circus.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/mvjj0UB</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Pokegeologist]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>#butlerianjihad</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/PwX4wwJ</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/l7GLeLm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/PwX4wwJ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Freyja33]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>ICE shoots priest in head with pepper ball</title><link>https://imgur.c